Insider Activity


Individual




Christopher B. Begley



Mr. Christopher B. Begley is Chairman at DeVry Education Group Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Hanger, Inc., Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc., Zimmer Biomet, Inc., Zimmer, Inc., Generic Pharmaceutical Association and The Executives Club of Chicago. Mr. Begley was previously employed as Non-Executive Chairman by The Hillshire Brands Co., Executive Chairman by Hospira, Inc., Vice President by MediSense, Inc., Senior Vice President-Hospital Products by Abbott Laboratories, Vice President-V Mueller Division Marketing by American Hospital Supply Corp., and Member-Civic Committee by Commercial Club Foundation. He also served on the board at Advanced Medical Technology Association, Economic Club of Chicago and National Center for Healthcare Leadership. He received his undergraduate degree from Western Illinois University and an MBA from Northern Illinois University.



